#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Multiple MongoDB Clients"
msgstr "多个 MongoDB 客户端"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"MongoDB allows you to configure multiple clients.\n"
"Using several clients works the same way as having a single client."
msgstr "MongoDB 允许您配置多个客户端。使用多个客户端的工作方式与使用单个客户端完全相同。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Notice there's an extra bit in the key (the `users` and `inventory` segments).\n"
"The syntax is as follows: `quarkus.mongodb.[optional name.][mongo connection property]`.\n"
"If the name is omitted, it configures the default client."
msgstr "请注意，该键中多了一个部分（即 `users` 和 `inventory` 段）。语法如下： `quarkus.mongodb.[可选名称.][Mongo 连接属性]` 。如果省略名称，则配置默认客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The use of multiple MongoDB clients enables multi-tenancy for MongoDB by allowing to connect to multiple MongoDB clusters. +\n"
"If you want to connect to multiple databases inside the same cluster,\n"
"multiple clients are **not** necessary as a single client is able to access all databases in the same cluster\n"
"(as a JDBC connection is able to access to multiple schemas inside the same database)."
msgstr ""
"通过使用多个 MongoDB 客户端，可以连接到多个 MongoDB 集群，从而实现 MongoDB 的多租户功能。\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"如果您想连接同一集群内的多个数据库， *则无需使用* 多个客户端，因为单个客户端即可访问同一集群中的所有数据库（就像 JDBC 连接可以访问同一数据库内的多个模式一样）。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Named Mongo client Injection"
msgstr "名为 Mongo 的客户端注入"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When using multiple clients, each `MongoClient`, you can select the client to inject using the `io.quarkus.mongodb.MongoClientName` qualifier.\n"
"Using the above properties to configure three different clients, you can also inject each one as follows:"
msgstr "当使用多个客户端（即多个 `MongoClient` ）时，您可以通过 `io.quarkus.mongodb.MongoClientName` 限定符来选择要注入的客户端。利用上述属性配置三个不同的客户端后，您还可以按以下方式注入每个客户端："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Activate or deactivate Mongo Clients"
msgstr "启用或禁用 Mongo 客户端"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When a Mongo Client is configured at build time, and its URL is set at runtime, it is active by default. Quarkus\n"
"starts the corresponding Mongo Client when the application starts."
msgstr "如果在构建时配置了 Mongo 客户端，且其 URL 在运行时被设置，则该客户端默认处于活动状态。Quarkus 会在应用程序启动时启动相应的 Mongo 客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To deactivate a Mongo Client at runtime, either:"
msgstr "要在运行时停用 Mongo 客户端，请执行以下任一操作："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Do not set `quarkus.mongodb[.optional name].hosts` or `quarkus.mongodb[.optional name].connection-#string#`."
msgstr "请勿设置 `quarkus.mongodb[.可选名称].hosts` 或 `quarkus.mongodb[.可选名称].connection-string` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Set `quarkus.mongodb[.optional name].active` to `false`."
msgstr "将 `quarkus.mongodb[.可选名称].active` 设置为 `false` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If a Mongo Client is not active:"
msgstr "如果 Mongo 客户端处于非活动状态："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Mongo Client does not attempt to connect to Mongo during application startup."
msgstr "Mongo 客户端不会在应用程序启动时尝试连接到 Mongo。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Mongo Client does not contribute a <<mongo-health-check,health check>>."
msgstr "Mongo 客户端不提供 xref:mongo-health-check[健康检查] 功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Static CDI injection points involving the Mongo Client, such as `@Inject ReactiveMongoClient mongoClient` or `@Inject MongoClient mongoClient`, cause application startup to fail."
msgstr "涉及 Mongo 客户端的静态 CDI 注入点（例如 `@Inject ReactiveMongoClient mongoClient` 或 `@Inject MongoClient mongoClient` ）会导致应用程序启动失败。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Dynamic retrieval of the Mongo Client, such as through `CDI.getBeanContainer()`, `Arc.instance()`, or an injected `Instance<ReactiveMongoClient>`, causes an exception to be thrown."
msgstr "通过动态方式获取 Mongo 客户端（例如通过 `CDI.getBeanContainer()` 、 `Arc.instance()` 或注入的 `Instance<ReactiveMongoClient>` ），会导致抛出异常。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Other Quarkus extensions that consume the Mongo Client may cause application startup to fail."
msgstr "其他使用 Mongo 客户端的 Quarkus 扩展可能会导致应用程序启动失败。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This feature is especially useful when the application must dynamically select a Mongo Client from a predefined set at\n"
"runtime."
msgstr "当应用程序必须在运行时从预定义的集合中动态选择一个 Mongo 客户端时，此功能特别有用。"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "An example of configuring multiple Mongo Clients for runtime selection:"
msgstr "以下是一个配置多个 Mongo 客户端以便在运行时进行选择的示例："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Setting `quarkus.mongodb.one.active=true` xref:config-reference.adoc#configuration-sources[at runtime] makes only the\n"
"Mongo Client `one` available.\n"
"Setting `quarkus.mongodb.two.active=true` at runtime makes only the Mongo Client `two` available."
msgstr "xref:config-reference.adoc#configuration-sources[在运行时] 将 `quarkus.mongodb.one.active` 设置 `为 true` ，将仅使 Mongo Client `one` 可用；在运行时将 `quarkus.mongodb.two.active` 设置为 `true，` 将仅使 Mongo Client `two` 可用。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A Mongo Client (either default or named) must always be discoverable at build-time to be considered for runtime\n"
"injection. This can be done by injecting the Mongo Client name with `@MongoClientName`. If the Mongo Client name may be\n"
"active or inactive, it needs to use the wrapper `InjectableInstance<>`, or else Quarkus will throw an exception at\n"
"startup time if the Mongo Client is inactive. Alternatively, Mongo Clients may also be discovered via configuration."
msgstr "Mongo 客户端（无论是默认的还是命名的）必须在构建时始终可被发现，才能被考虑进行运行时注入。这可以通过使用 `@MongoClientName` 注解注入 Mongo 客户端名称来实现。 如果 Mongo 客户端名称可能处于活动或非活动状态，则需要使用 `InjectableInstance<>` 包装器；否则，如果 Mongo 客户端处于非活动状态，Quarkus 将在启动时抛出异常。此外，Mongo 客户端也可以通过配置进行发现。"

